  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::DialogueObject
  dialogue:
  - "Good day Advisor. Chief Parker here.\n\nI wish we\u2019d be meeting in better
    circumstances. My subordinates are already at work examining the extent of the
    toxic waste and trying to track the source and history of the materials.\n\nDo
    not worry advisor. We will figure out the dastardly actors behind this."
  - "I\u2019ve taken the liberty of preparing protective gear for you so you may
    come see for yourself, Advisor. "
